   "source": [
    "using Polynomials\n",
    "q = fit(x,y,2);      # interpolating polynomial\n",
    "plot!(x->q(x),interval...,l=:dash,label=\"interpolant\",ylim=[-.1,3])"
   ]
  },

   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "To do inverse interpolation, we swap the roles of $x$ and $y$ in the interpolation."
   ]

   ]
